                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td><p align="center" class="hui_hang">板 凳 </p></td>
                        <td><p align="left" class="hui_hang">2对(含)以上连续对牌。如3344、445566。不包括2点和双王。 </p></td>
                        <td><p align="center" class="hui_hang">&nbsp;<img width="29" height="34" src="gandengyan_clip_image014.gif" />&nbsp;<img width="29" height="34" src="gandengyan_clip_image015.gif" />&nbsp;<img width="29" height="34" src="gandengyan_clip_image016.gif" />&nbsp;<img width="29" height="34" src="gandengyan_clip_image017.gif" /></p></td>
                      </tr>
